Author: mrlynch#5735
Content: as someone recently explained it to me ğŸ˜„

Author: mrlynch#5735
Content: it's based on the amounts of payments you received in your wallet

Author: mrlynch#5735
Content: let's say you have 5,000 ARRR in your wallet received in 500 transactions (different amounts)

Author: mrlynch#5735
Content: make an average per transaction -> 5000 / 500 = 10

Author: mrlynch#5735
Content: now multiply that by 54 (max tx's at once) -> 10 * 54 = 540

Author: mrlynch#5735
Content: and then use 80% as your send amount (to play it safe) -> 540 * 0.8 = 432

Author: mrlynch#5735
Content: that send would most likely (95% chance depending on what incoming utxo's are selected) go through

Author: mrlynch#5735
Content: that's the math, replace with your numbers
